        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>Think and reflect, how to make my life better?<br><a id="more"></a></p></blockquote><p>I encounter several fantastic quotes,</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;生命如此短暂, 我们没有时间去互相争吵, 道歉, 发泄, 责备, 时间只够用来去爱, 可它又只有一瞬, 令人惋惜!&quot;</span><br><span class="line">                                                                        </span><br><span class="line">                                                                           ——马克·吐温</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
